ify;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/3Modern%20Systems%20(K)%20Ltd\\/index.php\\/services\\/database-development\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/jd_newyork_astroid\\/database_development.png\\\" alt=\\\"database development\\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"70\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Database Development<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"sub-p2\\\">Database is the heart of a software application, database development services is quintessential to maintaining and nurturing relationship with prospects and customers<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-lg-4 col-md-6\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/3Modern%20Systems%20(K)%20Ltd\\/index.php\\/services\\/dedicated-virtual-team\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/jd_newyork_astroid\\/dedicated_virtual_team.png\\\" alt=\\\"dedicated virtual team\\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"70\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Dedicated Virtual Team<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"sub-p2\\\">Now you can maximize your profits with a dynamic dedicated virtual team which is committed to support you in all circumstances online sitting anywhere at any point of time<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-lg-4 col-md-6\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/3Modern%20Systems%20(K)%20Ltd\\/index.php\\/services\\/design-services\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/jd_newyork_astroid\\/design.png\\\" alt=\\\"design\\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"70\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Design Services<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"sub-p2\\\">Design is a form of art. However, IT Design is