\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"70\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Hire ASP.NET MVC Developers<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"sub-p2\\\">3Modern Kenya offers a wide fleet of professional .NET MVC developers with an experience of over thousand projects in the domain and all-round knowledge for accomplishing your tailor made needs<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-lg-4 col-md-6\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/3Modern%20Systems%20(K)%20Ltd\\/index.php\\/services\\/mobile-development\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/jd_newyork_astroid\\/androidios_developers.png\\\" alt=\\\"androidios developers\\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"35\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<h4 class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\">Hire iOS &amp; Android Developers<\\/h4>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\">3Modern Kenya can help you get a multi-platform business app for an increased ROI and outbound reach within the market through smartphone business channel<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-lg-4 col-md-6\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/3Modern%20Systems%20(K)%20Ltd\\/index.php\\/expertise\\/php-development\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"wt-w-ofr-inr\\\"><img src=\\\"images\\/jd_newyork_astroid\\/php.png\\\" alt=\\\"php\\\" width=\\\"70\\\" height=\\\"70\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" \\/>\\r\\n<h4 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Hire PHP Developers<\\/h4>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"sub-p2\\\">We offer a convenient PHP development services through our diligent PHP developers working day in and day out to meet your requirements within the crunch deadlines<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"col-lg-4 col-md-6\\\" style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\"><a href=\\\